A configurable template that displays a web map from ArcGIS.com and allows you to generate an elevation profile for a measured line.
This template is part of the ArcGIS.com template gallery. These templates can be accessed from the ArcGIS.com map viewer Share window or from the Web Application Templates group.
When accessed from the map viewer the templates can be published as a hosted application or you can download the template ZIP file to install on your web server.

This template uses the Elevation Analysis services available on ArcGIS Online.  To learn more about these services please visit https://developers.arcgis.com/en/rest/elevation/